item.title: By: owner2
item.dc:creator: owner2
item.description: The flat was very clean and perfectly in line with the pictures, close to arsenal station and very quiet. We will return definitely. Parking in front of the house. Perfect WiFi connection. A/C working well. Comfortable beds. Fruit, water and juice was present.
